Detailed Description

cvmx_nqm_vf::_nssr

NQM_VF(x)_NSSR is the NVMe-standard NVM subsystem reset (NSSR) CSR for function x. NQM_VF_MODE[VF_MODE] selects the functions that are actually present in the hardware. See NQM_VF_MODE_E.
